{"tid":965450,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[財技] 【大劉撐許家印】華置陪恒大自我加租 撐高大樓估值","createTime":"2019-01-02T05:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T10:37:27.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf3aedfc3f4a6ec34e052715856ad3918a09621","tid":965450,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"【大劉撐許家印】華置陪恒大自我加租 撐高大樓估值<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190102/59096010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190102%2F59096010&d=8bpNXnFkE57gNuvy2jcr2W6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f16337a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190102%2F59096010&h=e88479f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190102/59096010</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n華置（127）大股東劉鑾雄與恒大（3333）關係千絲萬縷，恒大為撐高前身為美國萬通大廈的恒大中心估值，「自我加租」3倍，華置亦陪同加租6成，令恒大中心估值升至225億元。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n《明報》取得恒大中心項目120億元貸融資的推介文件，其中指恒大中心今年租金收入增長83.4%至3.62億元，不過大幅增長原因為恒大、華置聯手泡製，雙方取消現有的恒大中心租約，再簽新約，並分別加租321%及64%。以恒大自行租用的93,119呎計算，呎租高達129元，較恒大中心的平均呎租約86元、或附近的夏慤大廈最新租賃成交的每呎52元都要高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">相比恒大、華置驚人的加租幅度，恒大中心其他租戶的加幅則相對合埋，如美國萬通加租9%、來寶集團加租8%。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n恒大於2015年向華置購入當時稱美國萬通大廈的恒大中心，作價125億，溢價25%，華置亦罕有地容許分期付款，恒大支付訂金12.5億及成交後支付37.5億，餘額於6年內每年支付12.5億元。"},{"pid":"8b4a3e9c041080931159225019145d355acd24d8","tid":965450,"uid":156363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T05:22:57.000Z","msg":"有錢佬話咁易就賺多幾廿億"},{"pid":"5e3a145e9562e2016e7fc59eef23ec8f4083daea","tid":965450,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6931332498f6659f4f7d880ac866c6b4c889a8","tid":965450,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"其實犯唔犯法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17b4b6a63c63156c924dc7ded85ff95b97aa5829","tid":965450,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"443bc4fab10d3670285d18fc40c4e36f1ea199a1","tid":965450,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T10:11:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f406047314d935d5c0738993f96e095a3b1be5dd","tid":965450,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d6931332498f6659f4f7d880ac866c6b4c889a8","tid":965450,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T06:34:21.000Z","msg":"其實犯唔犯法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T10:15:11.000Z","msg":"大把律師計住啦<br />\n<br />\n而且，香港政府邊敢郁有錢佬<br />\n<br />\n你睇法官見到富家子犯法都隻眼開隻眼閉"},{"pid":"179a4e6c4b7c1967311c3e3e9e95caf12993198f","tid":965450,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T10:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ede62deb6fbb6fc8ac3d567ed40884d5ae1db47","tid":965450,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T10:37:27.000Z","msg":"加租比自己， 甲戶口過數比乙戶口，再轉返比甲戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}